{"id": 732, "genre": 1001, "title": "2015年你看过的最后悔的电影是什么？", "description": "把钱还给老子，还有时间！（题图来自：Willian Santiago）", "record_count": 9522, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194601w7c2zGijgOHSpYRW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-01T01:00:53Z", "options": [{"id": 38912, "content": "煎饼侠，歌比电影好，后面的笑点超尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340883}, {"id": 38659, "content": "道士下山！", "image": null, "praise_count": 191, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360385}, {"id": 38660, "content": "说九层妖塔的都还没看训龙诀呢吧！两个都炒鸡烂！", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75473}, {"id": 38661, "content": "说聂隐娘和烈日灼心的脑子瓦特了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66449}, {"id": 39941, "content": "剩者为王！好的导演决定影片质量！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412995}, {"id": 38662, "content": "烈日灼心不烂吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180822}, {"id": 39430, "content": "火星救援", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407843}, {"id": 38663, "content": "恶棍天使，夏洛特烦恼，第三种爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401970}, {"id": 40711, "content": "何以笙箫默 真的是因为才9.9", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419324}, {"id": 38664, "content": "竟然没有钟馗伏魔吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323431}, {"id": 38920, "content": "什么什么好莱坞的吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403582}, {"id": 39176, "content": "九层妖塔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405667}, {"id": 45576, "content": "港囧，唯一一次宿舍所有人都去了影院，然而电影选择权不在我，只为了大家都在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 38921, "content": "怦然星动啊?真的是没钱了要接这种片嘛?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349464}, {"id": 40457, "content": "夏洛特烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417379}, {"id": 74762, "content": "夏洛克，看了电影好像有点不喜欢卷福了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598592}, {"id": 38666, "content": "邓超系列，这个原本不错的演员今年都不知道在干什么，喜剧和恶俗傻傻分不清楚", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319863}, {"id": 42250, "content": "京城八十一号 看完我就笑了这尼玛什么鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428279}, {"id": 38667, "content": "幸好我没看电影。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401977}, {"id": 38923, "content": "绝对是 第三种爱情……进了电影院我就睡着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403658}, {"id": 39179, "content": "钟馗伏魔！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405746}, {"id": 38668, "content": "栀子花开，怦然星动，九层妖塔，\n我居然看了这么多烂片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89306}, {"id": 38924, "content": "港囧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403577}, {"id": 41996, "content": "九层妖塔！！睡了一个多小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428170}, {"id": 38669, "content": "新闻联播", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400564}, {"id": 38925, "content": "九层妖塔，看过的中最烂的片，只因为其他的烂片都没去看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389702}, {"id": 38671, "content": "写师父的意思是：最后悔没去电影院看！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401987}, {"id": 38927, "content": "九层妖塔，妖怪糊了我一脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170456}, {"id": 39439, "content": "黄金时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407930}, {"id": 38672, "content": "说聂隐娘的不赞同，杨贵妃烂", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320634}, {"id": 38928, "content": "其实看影评也是一种乐趣，其实是提不起勇气去看国产大（烂）片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403708}, {"id": 40208, "content": "宅女侦探桂香", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415715}, {"id": 38673, "content": "故事里的故事的故事的故事的故事……又烂又长\n(《故事的故事》)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401998}, {"id": 38929, "content": "何以笙箫默 陪小妹妹去的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 373017}, {"id": 38674, "content": "一念天堂！不知所云", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402002}, {"id": 38930, "content": "火星救援，不知道为什么我睡着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157233}, {"id": 39186, "content": "九层妖塔啊，看到的只有贴着“我是特效”的各种特效，没谁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405826}, {"id": 38675, "content": "九层妖塔有头无尾。万万没想到没剧情无厘头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402008}, {"id": 38931, "content": "不觉得寻龙诀差?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359652}, {"id": 39443, "content": "恶棍天使", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407981}, {"id": 39188, "content": "分歧者2比1差多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403956}, {"id": 39444, "content": "前任攻略2，我没去电影院看，看了他觉得浪费了我的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407991}, {"id": 38677, "content": "一个勺子，看完你就是勺子", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258754}, {"id": 39189, "content": "九层妖塔…其他都完美避开了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319861}, {"id": 39957, "content": "老炮儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413151}, {"id": 38678, "content": "左耳", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325310}, {"id": 38934, "content": "我后悔没看心迷宫", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276118}, {"id": 38935, "content": "日本动作片，你懂得", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403762}, {"id": 39447, "content": "分手大师", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408003}, {"id": 39703, "content": "完美避开", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341457}]}